                    <p>An excellent reservation management tool is so useful in allowing guests to choose their preferred room when booking. Some sophisticated versions of reservation management systems enable guests to select extras like flowers, wines, fruits, and many more that they would want in the rooms they booked a reservation for online.  </p>
